<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="O" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Orbed" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Orbed,</orth> circular, round: <cit><quote>their poor balls are tied to the o. earth,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lc 25" default="NO" valid="yes">Compl. 25</bibl></cit>. <emph>that o. continent</emph> (the sun) <bibl n="shak. tn 5.278" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. V, 278</bibl>. <cit><quote>Tellus' o. ground,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.166" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 166</bibl></cit>.
